======================================================================
PE STUDY V2 — COMPREHENSIVE DEEP ANALYSIS
======================================================================
  Period: 2019-01-01 -> 2026-02-20   Warmup: 365d
  Cost: harsh (50 bps RT)
  Bootstrap: 2000 paths, block=60, seed=42

  Tests:
    1. VDO vs PE overlap analysis
    2. Component decomposition (CLV, BODY, zDV)
    3. PE* = BODY × max(0,zDV) — de-overlapped
    4. Entry window (PE only near EMA crossover)
    5. Q70 with 300-bar quantile window
    6. Multi-timescale consistency check
    7. Full 2000-path bootstrap on all promising variants

