    VDO=0, PE>0:      1733 ( 11.1%)
    Both ≤ 0:         6037 ( 38.6%)

  When VDO > 0 (7878 bars):
    P(CLV>0 | VDO>0) = 59.6%
    P(BODY>0.35 | VDO>0) = 55.8%
    P(zDV>0 | VDO>0) = 51.5%

